  <summary date="2020-07-09T22:22:02Z" status="Introduced in House">Buy America for Drinking Water Extension Act of 2019

This bill makes permanent a requirement that projects financed through a drinking water state revolving fund program only use iron and steel products that are produced in the United States, unless the Environmental Protection Agency grants a waiver from the requirement.</summary>
